response.overview: Trenggalek Regency is located in the southern part of East Java Province. It boasts many beautiful and captivating tourist attractions.  We focus on promoting lesser-known tourist destinations, such as the ones featured in this promotional video.  Trenggalek may be remote, but it also holds thousands of heavenly treasures.  Trenggalek, The Land of Paradise.
response.title: The Land of Paradise
